{
  "number": 56,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الوَاقِعَةِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Waaqia",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "When the Event inevitable cometh to pass,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Then will no (soul) entertain falsehood concerning its coming.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "(Many) will it bring low; (many) will it exalt;",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "When the earth shall be shaken to its depths,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "And the mountains shall be crumbled to atoms,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "Becoming dust scattered abroad,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "And ye shall be sorted out into three classes.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "Then (there will be) the Companions of the Right Hand;- What will be the Companions of the Right Hand?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "And the Companions of the Left Hand,- what will be the Companions of the Left Hand?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "And those Foremost (in Faith) will be Foremost (in the Hereafter).",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "These will be those Nearest to Allah:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "In Gardens of Bliss:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "A number of people from those of old,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "And a few from those of later times.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "(They will be) on Thrones encrusted (with gold and precious stones),",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Reclining on them, facing each other.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "Round about them will (serve) youths of perpetual (freshness),",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "With goblets, (shining) beakers, and cups (filled) out of clear-flowing fountains:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "No after-ache will they receive therefrom, nor will they suffer intoxication:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "And with fruits, any that they may select:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "And the flesh of fowls, any that they may desire.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "And (there will be) Companions with beautiful, big, and lustrous eyes,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "Like unto Pearls well-guarded.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "A Reward for the deeds of their past (life).",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "Not frivolity will they hear therein, nor any taint of ill,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "Only the saying, \"Peace! Peace\".",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "The Companions of the Right Hand,- what will be the Companions of the Right Hand?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "(They will be) among Lote-trees without thorns,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "Among Talh trees with flowers (or fruits) piled one above another,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "In shade long-extended,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "By water flowing constantly,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And fruit in abundance.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "Whose season is not limited, nor (supply) forbidden,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "And on Thrones (of Dignity), raised high.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "We have created (their Companions) of special creation.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "And made them virgin - pure (and undefiled), -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "Beloved (by nature), equal in age,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "For the Companions of the Right Hand.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "A (goodly) number from those of old,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "And a (goodly) number from those of later times.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "The Companions of the Left Hand,- what will be the Companions of the Left Hand?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "(They will be) in the midst of a Fierce Blast of Fire and in Boiling Water,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 43,
      "text": "And in the shades of Black Smoke:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 44,
      "text": "Nothing (will there be) to refresh, nor to please:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 45,
      "text": "For that they were wont to be indulged, before that, in wealth (and luxury),",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 46,
      "text": "And persisted obstinately in wickedness supreme!",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 47,
      "text": "And they used to say, \"What! when we die and become dust and bones, shall we then indeed be raised up again?-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 48,
      "text": "\"(We) and our fathers of old?\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 49,
      "text": "Say: \"Yea, those of old and those of later times,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 50,
      "text": "\"All will certainly be gathered together for the meeting appointed for a Day well-known.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 51,
      "text": "\"Then will ye truly,- O ye that go wrong, and treat (Truth) as Falsehood!-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 52,
      "text": "\"Ye will surely taste of the Tree of Zaqqum.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 53,
      "text": "\"Then will ye fill your insides therewith,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 54,
      "text": "\"And drink Boiling Water on top of it:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 55,
      "text": "\"Indeed ye shall drink like diseased camels raging with thirst!\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 56,
      "text": "Such will be their entertainment on the Day of Requital!",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 57,
      "text": "It is We Who have created you: why will ye not witness the Truth?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 58,
      "text": "Do ye then see?- The (human Seed) that ye throw out,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 59,
      "text": "Is it ye who create it, or are We the Creators?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 60,
      "text": "We have decreed Death to be your common lot, and We are not to be frustrated",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 61,
      "text": "from changing your Forms and creating you (again) in (forms) that ye know not.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 62,
      "text": "And ye certainly know already the first form of creation: why then do ye not celebrate His praises?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 63,
      "text": "See ye the seed that ye sow in the ground?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 64,
      "text": "Is it ye that cause it to grow, or are We the Cause?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 65,
      "text": "Were it Our Will, We could crumble it to dry powder, and ye would be left in wonderment,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 66,
      "text": "(Saying), \"We are indeed left with debts (for nothing):",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 67,
      "text": "\"Indeed are we shut out (of the fruits of our labour)\"",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 68,
      "text": "See ye the water which ye drink?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 69,
      "text": "Do ye bring it down (in rain) from the cloud or do We?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 70,
      "text": "Were it Our Will, We could make it salt (and unpalatable): then why do ye not give thanks?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 71,
      "text": "See ye the Fire which ye kindle?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 72,
      "text": "Is it ye who grow the tree which feeds the fire, or do We grow it?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 73,
      "text": "We have made it a memorial (of Our handiwork), and an article of comfort and convenience for the denizens of deserts.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 74,
      "text": "Then celebrate with praises the name of thy Lord, the Supreme!",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 75,
      "text": "Furthermore I call to witness the setting of the Stars,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 76,
      "text": "And that is indeed a mighty adjuration if ye but knew,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 77,
      "text": "That this is indeed a qur'an Most Honourable,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 78,
      "text": "In Book well-guarded,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 79,
      "text": "Which none shall touch but those who are clean:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 80,
      "text": "A Revelation from the Lord of the Worlds.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 81,
      "text": "Is it such a Message that ye would hold in light esteem?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 82,
      "text": "And have ye made it your livelihood that ye should declare it false?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 83,
      "text": "Then why do ye not (intervene) when (the soul of the dying man) reaches the throat,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 84,
      "text": "And ye the while (sit) looking on,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 85,
      "text": "But We are nearer to him than ye, and yet see not,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 86,
      "text": "Then why do ye not,- If you are exempt from (future) account,-",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 87,
      "text": "Call back the soul, if ye are true (in the claim of independence)?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 88,
      "text": "Thus, then, if he be of those Nearest to Allah,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 89,
      "text": "(There is for him) Rest and Satisfaction, and a Garden of Delights.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 90,
      "text": "And if he be of the Companions of the Right Hand,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 91,
      "text": "(For him is the salutation), \"Peace be unto thee\", from the Companions of the Right Hand.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 92,
      "text": "And if he be of those who treat (Truth) as Falsehood, who go wrong,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
